<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSalomon.2C_Frank.3B_and_Renata_Peters">Salomon, Frank; and Renata Peters (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2007-03-31"><a href="/wiki/2007" title="2007">2007</a>-<a href="/wiki/March_31" title="March 31">03-31</a></span>) (with collaboration of Carrie Brezine, Gino de las Casas Ríos, Víctor Falcón Huayta, Rosa Choque Gonzales, and Rosalía Choque Gonzales). <i>Governance and Conservation of the Rapaz Khipu Patrimony</i>. paper delivered at Interdisciplinary Workshop on Intangible Heritage. Collaborative for Cultural Heritage and Museum Practices, Urbana-Champaign, IL.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Governance+and+Conservation+of+the+Rapaz+Khipu+Patrimony&amp;rft.aulast=Salomon%2C+Frank%3B+and+Renata+Peters&amp;rft.au=Salomon%2C+Frank%3B+and+Renata+Peters&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2007-03-31%5D%5D&amp;rft.series=paper+delivered+at+Interdisciplinary+Workshop+on+Intangible+Heritage&amp;rft.pub=Collaborative+for+Cultural+Heritage+and+Museum+Practices%2C+Urbana-Champaign%2C+IL&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Quipu"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFUrton1998"><a href="/wiki/Gary_Urton" title="Gary Urton">Urton, Gary</a> (1998). "From Knots to Narratives: Reconstructing the Art of Historical Record Keeping in the Andes from Spanish Transcriptions of Inka <i>Khipus</i>". <i>Ethnohistory</i> <b>45</b> (5): 409. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F483319" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F483319" rel="nofollow">10.2307/483319</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/issn/0014-1801" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/issn/0014-1801" rel="nofollow">0014-1801</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=From+Knots+to+Narratives%3A+Reconstructing+the+Art+of+Historical+Record+Keeping+in+the+Andes+from+Spanish+Transcriptions+of+Inka+%27%27Khipus%27%27&amp;rft.jtitle=Ethnohistory&amp;rft.aulast=Urton&amp;rft.aufirst=Gary&amp;rft.au=Urton%2C+Gary&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.volume=45&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=409&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F483319&amp;rft.issn=0014-1801&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Quipu"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
